  "notes": [
    "This case report describes two different mechanisms for junctional rhythm: preoperative (escaped beat due to primary pacemaker slowing) and intraoperative (accelerated due to adrenaline-induced sympathetic activity)",
    "The paper emphasizes the importance of identifying the underlying cause of junctional rhythm for appropriate anesthetic management"
